The White House




June 16, 2009

 



Schedule Of Judge Sotomayors Capitol Hill Meetings Today 06/16/2009




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary  ______________________________________________________________________  FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                                                June 16, 2009  SCHEDULE OF JUDGE SOTOMAYOR’S CAPITOL HILL MEETINGS  TUESDAY, JUNE 16  Today, Judge Sotomayor will visit Capitol Hill to meet with the following Senators: Senator Jeff Bingaman  Senator Tom Carper  Senator Thad Cochran  Senator Mike Crapo  Senator Frank Lautenberg  Senator Tom Udall   ##
